<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>898</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>rú jīn wǒ bǎ nǐ men jiāo tuō shén 迦南898</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 rú jīn wǒ bǎ nǐ men jiāo tuō shén, hé tā ēn huì de dào.
 zhè dào néng jiàn lì nǐ men, gēn jī wěn gù, fēng chuī yǔ dǎ bù huì dòng yáo.
 zhè dào néng jiào nǐ men hé yī qiè chéng shèng de rén, tóng dé yǒng héng de jī yè.
 zhè dào néng jiù nǐ men chū lí hēi àn, zhǎo dào shēng mìng de yī kào.
 shǒu zhe zhè dào, shǒu zhe zhè dào, fēng chuī yǔ dǎ yě bù huì dòng yáo.
 zhè dào néng bǎo shǒu nǐ yī lù píng ān, yī shēng bù huì shī jiǎo.</lyrics>
</song>